#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an10.68:6.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā paccuṭṭhāya āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then the Buddha got up and said to Venerable Sāriputta:"

msgctxt "an10.68:6.2"
msgid "“sādhu sādhu, sāriputta."
msgstr "“Good, good, Sāriputta!"

